quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  31,1,"Alif-lam-meem"
  31,2,"Tilka ayatu alkitabi alhakeem"
  31,3,"Hudan warahmatan lilmuhsineen"
  31,4,"Allatheena yuqeemoona assalatawayu/toona azzakata wahum bil-akhiratihum yooqinoon"
  31,5,"Ola-ika AAala hudan minrabbihim waola-ika humu almuflihoon"
  31,6,"Wamina annasi man yashtareelahwa alhadeethi liyudilla AAan sabeeli Allahibighayri AAilmin wayattakhithaha huzuwan ola-ikalahum AAathabun muheen"
  31,7,"Wa-itha tutla AAalayhi ayatunawalla mustakbiran kaan lam yasmaAAha kaanna fee othunayhiwaqran fabashshirhu biAAathabin aleem"
  31,8,"Inna allatheena amanoowaAAamiloo assalihati lahum jannatuannaAAeem"
  31,9,"Khalideena feeha waAAda Allahihaqqan wahuwa alAAazeezu alhakeem"
  31,10,"Khalaqa assamawatibighayri AAamadin tarawnaha waalqa fee al-ardirawasiya an tameeda bikum wabaththa feeha min kullidabbatin waanzalna mina assama-i maanfaanbatna feeha min kulli zawjin kareem"